contentBody:
**Difficulty**: Medium
**Type**: MSQ (Multiple Select Question)
**Category**: Application

---


A developer is building a restaurant website and writes the following CSS. Which statements about this code are **correct**? Select ALL that apply.

```css
.restaurant-header {
  text-align: center;
}

.menu-section h2 {
  text-align: left;
}

.menu-section p {
  text-align: justify;
}

.price {
  text-align: right;
}

footer p {
  text-align: center;
}
```
